Ok So...I am a flaming homo and I do dress like a lil boy...a cute one hehe Neways Yesterday I had sex...with a boy wow...and I dressed like a girl with spikey blonde hair. I just had to write this down cuz who knows when It will happen again! 

I would just like to say moms keyboard sucks ass cuz I have to type one word 8 times just becuz half the keys dont work and I have to go back and push them 100 times to make it work LoL 

I went to work with my uncle last night. Hes a cop and well it was a interesting night...I got hit on by a mexican transvestite who spoke very little english. Then I had to help load this 500lb man into a ambulace who had fell and broke his leg and hit his head on a table..But he was ok by the end of the night. 

DOOD I NEED A JOB...I just wanted to announce that...:/ Oh yeah and I need a car too! 

Neways uhm other then that not much is new...the 32 year old psycho lesbian is still chasing after me...and Im still running away...do you not see a hint? Apparently she doesnt! Mom's still bitchy 3/4's of the day and the 1/4 shes not bitchy is the time when shes asleep :x My battle called me today. Its her 21st birthday...I miss her so much :/ Had she not been a confused girl who didnt want to disapoint her parents I think I would of married her =/ But were still like best friends. OK I've said enough for today...leave one and I'll holla baaacckkk...no Im not under the influence! And for the record I slept until 3:00 this afternoon! yay go me

Ok...So Trisha decided that I needed this thing...so she made it for me...so I suppose I HAVE to write in it now hehe So yeah me and her are going to see LIT this coming weekend. Im pretty excited. Shes about the only person I havnt been able to see since I got back home :/ 

So Crystal and Jennefer are having major problems. Its kind of weird talking to both of them. I talked to Crystal alot this morning. It was like the first time we've really talked in about 4 months. She just told me how she felt and how Jennefer's making her feel, and Seeing as how I've been with Jennefer and Crystal I understand alot about this situation because I know how both people act in certain situations....Crystal wants to talk....Jennefer likes to run away. It just goes in a little circle. I think they both just need to talk. I told Crystal this morning how I know I fucked up the relationship between the two of us...and I admit to my wrong...and all the times she use to cuss me out on the phone about it I just wanted to make her shut the fuck up. But thats because I was only thinking about how her cussing me out made me feel, not how I was making her feel. So I made myself listen to what she had to say and it not only made me see things differently about the two of us but it made me look back on me as a person too. I think maybe for that second I got her to see that I have done alot of thinking...she seemed kind of shocked and said she didnt know I felt that way...but thats because we never talk anymore so I cant tell her how I feel. *shrugs* Maybe one day will be able to talk more...I hope...shes a good person to have in your life..even if its just as my friend. 

Hmm I've moved back in with mom. BIG MISTAKE. We fight like 2 5 year olds over the last M&M in the bag. Im trying to find a job..and within the next 3 or 4 months or so I want to move out..get some roomates or something yanno? Well see what happens...

So yeah I think I've wrote enough for today...or atleast for right now...I have to go find my Dr. Pepper....I have lost it again :/ TaTa ~LiL Moe~
